    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat</p><p>Once very hot, add your <strong>beef mince</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until browned all over, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
