    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the beef is sticky, remove the pan from the heat, sprinkle over your <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame seeds</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>sticky sesame beef mince stir-fry</strong></p>",
